description:
Danny recaps this week's Real Housewives of Salt Lake City, which featured a hip-hop/golf surprise party, a Galentine's event, and more! On the Real Housewives of Dallas premiere, we're introduced to the new Housewife, Tiffany Moon.


RHOD Recap: 29:00ish
